Every month, we give away one unique, beautiful and luscious dunnie. Here is how to win: 

When we post our new (h3h3production, main channel) videos on Facebook and Twitter, all you need to do is LIKE AND SHARE/RETWEET each video to be eligible to win. The more you like/share, the higher chance you have of winning.

At the end of every month we will announce the winner on the "Ethan and Hila" channel and message you on Facebook or Twitter.
